data.description: If you are looking for a hidden gem with lots of privacy, you just found it! Sits on a over an acre of land. Very Private. Great location. Not in City limits.  Lots of room for Huge Pole Barn or an in-ground pool or a tennis court. Plenty of room to expand the house itself and add a huge deck  Two (2) bedrooms with 2 full baths. Lovely bright den/family room which leads out onto a rear deck.  New HVAC & Condenser in 2022. All new Windows installed in 2022 Garage was converted by a previous owner into useable space. Seller used it as his art studio and storage. Can be converted back to a garage if you so desire. House being professionally cleaned.  Schedule your private showing.
